__________________________________________
|Class Jbutton
|__________________________________________
|Board : array(3x3x8) 
|	stores possible
|	wins and tie if board is full
|__________________________________________
|Action method - 
|	player clicks [left, middle, right] 
|		[top, middle, bottom]
|	action method will add the icon to 
|		the box
|End method - 
|	button to end the class
|__________________________________________



